org.wallerlab.yoink.api.model.molecular

Enum Element

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.lang.Enum<Element>
      • org.wallerlab.yoink.api.model.molecular.Element
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable, java.lang.Comparable<Element>

    public enum Element
extends java.lang.Enum<Element>
    Enum Element(c1, c2, c3, z1, z2, z3,atomMass,atomNumber). c1, c2, c3, z1, z2 and z3 are parameters for numerical LSDA free-atomic densities for the neutral atoms H to Ar. For numerical LSDA free-atomic densities, see: Perdew, J. P.; Wang, Y. Phys. Rev. B 1992, 45, 13244
